headline: Keysight Enables Samsung Electronics to Validate FiRa® 2.0 Secure Ranging Test Cases
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., November 13, 2024--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) has enabled Samsung Electronics to validate FiRa® 2.0 secure test cases on its Exynos Connect U100 chipset. This was achieved using Keysight’s Ultra-Wideband (UWB) test solution, which meets the requirements needed for physical layer conformance testing.

headline: KEYS Set to Report Q4 Results: Will Top-Line Decline Impede Earnings?
summary: Keysight expects to report a revenue contraction year over year in the fiscal fourth quarter, owing to weakness in several verticals.
